{"tid":1890634,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE周子瑜趴地自拍　網揪亮點萌翻啦！","createTime":"2020-02-21T09:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T13:19:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"251937c86e06662bc2d2709685ab5c20ab418364","tid":1890634,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:52:44.000Z","msg":"韓國女團TWICE成員周子瑜在團體中相當亮眼，除了擁有精緻的臉蛋外，高挑身材比例更是一絕。不過日前TWICE官方IG曝光一組她的照片，照片中她還趴著自拍，網友也意外發現亮點。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE官方IG今天曝光一組周子瑜的生活日常照，她先是曝光自己的愛狗，接著還放了張聚餐的佳餚照，而讓網友們最驚訝的莫過於是自拍照啦。照片中只見子瑜趴在地上，一面抓著頭髮一面看著鏡頭，但許多網友卻被她身旁的黑貓萌暈，紛紛直呼：「貓怎麼扁了」、「真的好扁」、「好可愛的貓咪耶」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/02/21/99/7497024.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F02%2F21%2F99%2F7497024.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=30ff0afb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/02/21/99/7497026.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F02%2F21%2F99%2F7497026.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=4b9cd343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/02/21/99/7497028.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F02%2F21%2F99%2F7497028.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=f0c6d92a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://stars.udn.co